\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 [1] FLINK KEYED STATE (RocksDB)
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0Purpose: Hot, streaming enrichment context
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0Scope: Active encounters + recent history (7-30 days)
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0Contents:
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\uc0\u10003  Current encounter details
