\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\uc0\u10003  Recent vitals (sliding window: 24h)
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\uc0\u10003  Active conditions
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\uc0\u10003  Allergies
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\uc0\u10003  Clinical scores (calculated)
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\uc0\u10007  Historical encounters (older than TTL)
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\uc0\u10007  Complete medication history
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\uc0\u10007  Longitudinal trends
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0Access Pattern: O(1) in-memory lookup
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0Update Pattern: Every incoming event
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0Persistence: Checkpoint to S3 (disaster recovery)
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0TTL: 7-30 days after encounter close
\f1\fs24 \
\

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 [2] FHIR STORE (PostgreSQL/MongoDB)
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0Purpose: Standards-compliant clinical data repository
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0Scope: Complete patient clinical record (longitudinal)
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0Contents:
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\uc0\u10003  All FHIR resources (Patient, Encounter, Observation, etc.)
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\uc0\u10003  Complete medication history
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\uc0\u10003  All lab results (with trend data)
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\uc0\u10003  All encounters (historical)
