\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0Update Pattern: Batch writes on encounter close
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0Query Example:
